'''图哈人'''（{{lang-tyv|Туха}}，{{lang|la|''Tuha''}}；{{lang-ru|Духа}}，{{lang|la|''Dukha''}}），常误译作'''杜科哈人'''{{noteTag|1={{lang|la|kh}}为一个辅音，发[[清软颚擦音|清软颚擦音]]，而非k音与h音连在一起。}}，是一个生活在[[蒙古国|蒙古国]][[库苏古尔省|库苏古尔省]]境内以饲养[[驯鹿|驯鹿]]为生的[[突厥语族|突厥语]]民族；蒙古人称之为'''察坦人'''或'''查唐人'''（{{lang-mn|Цаатан}}, ''Tsaatan''），意为“驯鹿牧民”。<ref>{{cite thesis|degree=M.A.|title=Lords of the Mongolian Taiga: An Ethnohistory of the Dukha Reindeer Herders|url=http://dlc.dlib.indiana.edu/dlc/bitstream/handle/10535/8294/Wheeler%202000--Lords%20of%20the%20Mongolian%20Taiga--Dukha%20Ethnohistory.pdf|last=Wheeler|first=W. Alan|year=2000|publisher=Indiana University|access-date=2016-11-18|archive-date=2016-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161029044132/http://dlc.dlib.indiana.edu/dlc/bitstream/handle/10535/8294/Wheeler%202000--Lords%20of%20the%20Mongolian%20Taiga--Dukha%20Ethnohistory.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>本民族语言图哈语与[[图瓦语|图瓦语]]相近，使用人数仅100-200人，为濒危语言。<ref>{{cite book|last=Salminen|first=Tapani|editor=Moseley, Christopher|title=Encyclopedia of the World's Endangered Languages|url=https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaworl00mose_636|year=2007|publisher=Routledge|location=Abingdon|isbn=978-0-7007-1197-0|pages=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaworl00mose_636/page/n261 243]|chapter=3 Europe and North Asia}}</ref>

